Here's my suggestion for the new faction.

The Silver Wings are a more militant branch of the Maximal Army that 
left when they realized that the Maximals would only cower in the 
safety of Earth. They want to get rid of the Tripreds, and the end 
justifies the mean. If it means collaborating with outlaws or 
renegades, so be it...
